                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Nous n'avons demandé le secours d'aucun roi ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Mais on te peut tout dire et confier, à toi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Soldat républicain, cœur loyal, homme juste",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Dont rien n'a pu lasser le dévoûment robuste.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Nous sommes en danger, Garibaldi ! Depuis",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Deux sombres mois plus noirs et plus lourds que les nuits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "L'invasion est là, piétinant sur la France.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Cris de rage, sanglots qu'arrache la souffrance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Voilà ce qu'on entend sur le sol désolé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "De ce pays, hier encor, joyeux, ailé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Qui, par toutes ses voix, malgré son maître immonde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Chantant la liberté, régénérait le monde.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Mêlant un nouveau crime à leurs crimes anciens,",
