                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Les Corses ont livré la France aux Prussiens ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "La lutte est douloureuse, et l'ogre en son repaire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Rit de joie, en voyant que plus d'un désespère.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "À notre aide, ô héros ! à notre aide ! Viens-t-en",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Parmi nous, et surgis, victorieux Titan,",
