                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Toi seul ! Cela suffit pour rendre le courage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "À qui pouvait douter, et raffermir encor",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Les vaillants dont l'audace est la cuirasse d'or.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "« Ce qui reste de moi, disais-tu, je le donne. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Merci, nous acceptons cette splendide aumône.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Ce qui reste de toi, preux sauveur ! C'est l'amour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "C'est l'abnégation, c'est la foi sans retour",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Dans la liberté sainte et l'auguste justice.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Tu fais évanouir toute gloire factice,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ton nom veut dire Exemple et veut dire Devoir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Nos soldats de vingt ans, guerrier, n'ont qu'à te voir",
