                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Pour monter au niveau de leurs aînés stoïques ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Bénis leurs jeunes fronts de tes mains héroïques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Et Marceau sortira de leurs rangs. Ton nom seul",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Faisait battre nos cœurs déjà sous le linceul",
